name: Rocket Launcher - Project Boost - Prototype
description:
Not made for Mobile Controls !! 

A simple rocket that needs to reach the target position after passing through the hurdles.

Controls: 
Space to give Thrust
Left and Right arrow Keys to rotate in the respective direction.
